game.name: Anna Picnic Day
game.description:
Beautiful Anna and handsome Kristoff have got married several years before and now they have a cute daughter. Today the weather is extremely lovely, so the couple has made out a plan to take her little daughter for an outing. Yes, it is a picnic party to their beach where they want to enjoy the awesome weather of today. But, they are confused what to pick or what to leave. Would you accept this offer to guide them? Join Anna Picnic Day game and be prepared to make all the arrangements they need for the picnic party!
You will find all the items on the screen in this brand new dressing game for girls. Your objective is to help them to dress up with the elegant clothes and also prepare some food before leaving the home. Choose the right hairstyle for Anna and combine it with a lovely full length outfit! Give her a complete pink color full-length middy or a blue and white color top combined with a green color jacket and a blue color skirt! Give her right hand a glass of drink and then move to dress up Kristoff in this html5 princess fun game!
Give him a light blue color short kurta combined with a dark blue color jacket and jean or a light chocolate color kurta combined with dark chocolate color pant! Do not forget to give a glass of drink in his hands to complete his picnic look. The little daughter also needs a makeover. So, select a nice outfit for her by clicking the dress options given on top of the screen. Feel free to change the background to give their party a complete picnic look! Make sure to select the needful eating items for them.
